      <p><strong>Wayne Crowe</strong> is a British entrepreneur and affiliate marketer who founded the OLSP System and operates the Traffic Dominators brand. He is presented in official materials and independent write-ups as a long-time affiliate marketer with substantial personal earnings in the MMO space, though specific income figures are vendor-reported and not independently verified. The OLSP System launched as a funnel-based affiliate commission platform and has evolved to include multiple traffic and tool offerings — of which solo ads are one component alongside the Traffic Rotator, TD Pages, and other products.</p>

      <p>The solo ad service predates some of the more recent OLSP product additions and appears to have been a core revenue stream for Wayne Crowe's Traffic Dominators brand before OLSP's current form. The service has operated under both the Traffic Dominators and OLSP brand identities, with the current primary commercial presence at soloads.olspsystem.com and products.olspsystem.com. A publicly documented solo ads training live session from July 2021 confirms the service has been active for at least five years as of this writing.</p>

      <p>OLSP's broader ecosystem has been described in independent reviews as involving heavy upsells and MLM-style commission structures — critiques that apply to the platform rather than to solo ads specifically. The solo ad product is a standalone traffic service and can be purchased without engaging with OLSP's affiliate commission tiers, though the two are closely intertwined in how the vendor markets them to members.</p>
