      <h3>Best For</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Existing OLSP members who have their Magick Link or Mega Link funnels active and ready, and need to accelerate traffic flow without building an audience organically from scratch.</li>
        <li>Affiliate marketers in the MMO/Biz Opp niche who have tested a conversion funnel with other traffic sources and want to scale using a vendor-direct solo ad service rather than navigating a marketplace.</li>
        <li>Marketers who want supplementary traffic for list-building campaigns and understand that purchased traffic needs a solid opt-in page, email sequence, and back-end offer to convert profitably.</li>
