      <h3>Skip If</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You don't yet have a tested opt-in page or funnel. Buying traffic before having a proven conversion mechanism in place is a reliable way to spend budget without results — the vendor's own training acknowledges this directly.</li>
        <li>Your offer is outside the Biz Opp/MMO niche. The Traffic Dominators list is built for this vertical. E-commerce products, B2B services, or content-based offers will likely be poorly matched to subscriber intent.</li>
        <li>You require independently audited traffic quality data before committing spend. No third-party audit of OLSP Solo Ads' Tier-1 percentages or list composition exists publicly.</li>
